org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.queue

Class JobInfoCallable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.queue.JobInfoCallable<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callable<T>, JobInfo

    public class JobInfoCallable<T>
extends Object
implements Callable<T>, JobInfo
    A callable computing job statistics. The job is given as another callable. The statistics are global, so must be used carefully.
